      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAST FELIX (2) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 29.88 beating Hey Jett. Has a low draw and in form and has the ability. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can continue on his winning ways. SHE'S SEEKING (1) looks close to another win after hitting the frame in a 5 length third (19.69) in a Grade 5 at Hobart. Form from her last run is proving very strong. Deserves a win and gets her chance. MERCEDES DANGER (3) was well in the market last time but only managed fourth (19.81), beaten 6 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. DAY RELEASE (6) can measure up with the right run.",
